NOTICE

This MIT license covers only the build scripts and documentation in this
repository. It does not extend to any third-party content the build scripts
extract or copy at runtime.

In particular:

  - Imagination Technologies' PowerVR userspace libraries (libsrv_um.so,
    libVK_IMG.so, libpvr_dri_support.so, libGLESv*_PVR_MESA.so, libPVROCL.so,
    libPVRScopeServices.so, etc., the contents of /usr/local/lib/{libEGL,
    libGLESv*,libgbm,libglapi,libvulkan}.so* shipped by Radxa, and PowerVR
    firmware blobs rgx.fw.* / rgx.sh.*): proprietary, distributed by
    Imagination/Radxa under their own EULAs.

  - Allwinner Technology's CedarC video userspace libraries (libVE.so,
    libcdc_base.so, libvdecoder.so, libvencoder.so, libaw*.so per-codec
    libraries, libOmx*.so, libMemAdapter.so, libfbm.so, libsbm.so,
    libscaledown.so, etc.): proprietary, distributed by Allwinner/Radxa
    under their own EULAs.

These build scripts neither include nor redistribute those binaries. They
operate by mounting a Radxa OS image that the user downloads themselves from
the official Radxa source, copying files out of that image into a derived
output image at build time on the user's own machine. The output image is for
the user's personal use; whether redistribution of the resulting image is
permissible is governed by Imagination's, Allwinner's, and Radxa's licenses,
not by this MIT license.
